- [ ] Map extensions → Brainfuck
- [ ] Emit valid Brainfuck

---

Phase 2 — Virtual Machine

- [ ] Implement bytecode interpreter in Brainfuck
- [ ] Define instruction set
- [ ] Build execution loop

---

Phase 3 — Virtual OS

- [ ] Implement syscall layer
- [ ] Add simple shell
- [ ] Load programs from memory

---

Phase 4 — “Linux-like” Environment

- [ ] File system abstraction
- [ ] Multi-program execution
- [ ] Scriptable environment

