🧱 Example (bfFS → Brainfuck)

Filesystem

/program/
  0001_inc.bf+
  0002_inc.bf+
  0003_loop.loop/
    0001_move.ptrr
    0002_print.out
  0004_loop.end/

Output

++[>.]

---

⚠️ Constraints

- Brainfuck performance is extremely limited
- VM inside Brainfuck is very slow
- Large systems will be difficult to debug
- True Linux compatibility is not feasible

---

🚀 Long-Term Vision

- A filesystem-native programming model
- A Brainfuck-hosted virtual machine
- A minimal Linux-like environment encoded structurally

---

🔥 Stretch Goals

- [ ] Self-hosting bfFS compiler
- [ ] Fully interactive shell inside Brainfuck VM
- [ ] Virtual process scheduler
- [ ] Load and run compiled bytecode programs
- [ ] Experimental “Brainfuck OS”

